Package org.eclipse.m2m.atl.common.ATL

Interface ATLPackage.Literals

Enclosing class:
ATLPackage
public static interface ATLPackage.Literals
Defines literals for the meta objects that represent
  • each class,
  • each feature of each class,
  • each enum,
  • and each data type
